  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to gssdp</title>

    <para>The <application>gssdp</application> package provides a GObject-based API
    for handling resource discovery and announcement over SSDP (Simple Service Discovery
    Protocol).</para>

    &lfs70_built;

